# REQ-PDD-002 positive fixture
# A PddSectionBReport that conforms to ReqPdd002Shape:
#   - references a quantification methodology (nias-o:usesMethodology)
#   - declares at least one impact (nias-o:hasDeclaredImpact)
#   - each declared impact has an impact benefit classification (nias-o:beneficialOrAdverse)

@prefix aiao: <http://w3id.org/aiao#> .
@prefix claimont: <http://w3id.org/claimont#> .
@prefix impactont: <http://w3id.org/impactont#> .
@prefix meth: <http://independentimpact.org/methodology/> .
@prefix nias-cs: <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/> .
@prefix nias-o: <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/> .
@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-methodology>
    a meth:Methodology ;
    rdfs:label "VVS Test Methodology 1.0" .

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-impact>
    a impactont:Impact ;
    nias-o:beneficialOrAdverse nias-cs:beneficial .

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-project>
    a aiao:Project .

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-report>
    a nias-o:PddSectionBReport ;
    claimont:isMadeBy <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/developer-1> ;
    claimont:hasSubject <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-project> ;
    nias-o:usesMethodology <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-methodology> ;
    nias-o:hasDeclaredImpact <https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/pdd-b-valid-impact> .

<https://nova.org.za/novaimpactaccountingstandard/vvs/fixtures/developer-1>
    a nias-o:PlatformUser .
